org.wikirate4j.entitities

Interface Company

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Card
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompanyImpl

    public interface Company
extends Card
    As Company, Wikirate, considers any formal reporting organization (including corporations, NGOs, Universities etc.). The Company entity extends the notion of a Card to provide additional information and functionality..
